summary: I've been recently very busy, actually I put all my time into work. I think I need to balanced mt working hours and time for my...
caption:
I’ve been recently very busy, actually I put all my time into work. I think I need to balanced mt working hours and time for my interests and also for my own projects ;w;
I’ve started from learning how to use TVpaint, I know many great animators use this software. I didn’t put much effort to this animation because I only have demo version ov TVpaint and it doesn’t allow to export and save projects, so it would be a pitty to discard my work xD

So “how you were able to do this gif?"you may ask. I simply do print screen of each frame xD

blog.name: asktheaggretsukofam
blog.title: Ask This Family Anything!
blog.description:
Hi! This will be a place where you can ask questions to Retsuko, Haida, and Ikari! And Fenneko, if you wish.

Based on the stories of @kingdomofkitten (who is also the one behind this page)

summary:
Retsuko: Is...is this thing on?
Haida: I think so! Fenneko, what’s the status?
Fenneko: Looks like we are good to go,...
body:
Retsuko: Is…is this thing on?

Haida: I think so! Fenneko, what’s the status?

Fenneko: Looks like we are good to go, guys.

Ikari: Igabagoo?

Retsuko: Not now, sweetie. Erm, hi, everyone! So, @kingdomofkitten, writer of this whole…Ikari-verse, I guess you could call it, has decided to put together this asking blog for us! So, if you want to ask us anything, you can!

Fenneko: How loving and generous our god is…and yet too lazy to work on the Wedding arc. :3

KingdomOfKitten: I’M WORKING ON IT!

Fenneko: Sure, bro. Sure.

Haida: …erm, in any case, just give us a question, and we’ll be sure to get back to you, if we feel the question is worth answering.

Ikari: Dabaaaa!

Fenneko: I think the kid’s asking you guys to send your questions. Could be wrong, could just be hungry.

Retsuko: Well, in that case. If you’ll excuse us, we have to feed this little munchkin. *picks up Ikari* But for real! Send those questions our way! :)

Haida: Thanks, guys!

summary: I guess I might as well promote this, but uh, I made a spin-off blog! This is where, if you happen to have questions to Retsuko,...
body:
I guess I might as well promote this, but uh, I made a spin-off blog! This is where, if you happen to have questions to Retsuko, Haida, Fenneko, or even little Ikari, you can ask! (for the record, the last one will probably have to be translated by the parents….or at least, an attempt. :P) I haven’t gotten questions yet, and I’m currently in the process of writing the wedding arc, but if you want to start asking, feel free! I might be able to answer a few! :)

https://asktheaggretsukofam.tumblr.com/

Background art in the blog is done by @helthehatter, and the profile pic is done by @skeletonguys-and-ragdolls, just in case anyone happens to be curious. ^^
